{"id":64,"parent_id":48,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":64,"title":"Luke 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"Luke","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus gives the parable of the unjust steward—He teaches of service and condemns divorce—He gives the parable of the rich man and Lazarus."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.1","order":"03.05.016.7831"},["b","1"],"And he said also unto his disciples, There was a certain rich man, which had a steward; and the same was accused unto him that he had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"wasted"],"his goods."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.2","order":"03.05.016.7832"},["b","2"],"And he called him, and said unto him, How is it that I hear this of thee? give an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"account"],"of thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"stewardship"],"; for thou mayest be no longer steward."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.3","order":"03.05.016.7833"},["b","3"],"Then the steward said within himself, What shall I do? for my lord taketh away from me the stewardship: I cannot dig; to beg I am ashamed."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.4","order":"03.05.016.7834"},["b","4"],"I am resolved what to do, that, when I am put out of the stewardship, they may receive me into their houses."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.5","order":"03.05.016.7835"},["b","5"],"So he called every one of his lord’s debtors",["i","unto him,"],"and said unto the first, How much owest thou unto my lord?"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.6","order":"03.05.016.7836"},["b","6"],"And he said, An hundred measures of oil. And he said unto him, Take thy bill, and sit down quickly, and write fifty."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.7","order":"03.05.016.7837"},["b","7"],"Then said he to another, And how much owest thou? And he said, An hundred measures of wheat. And he said unto him, Take thy bill, and write fourscore."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.8","order":"03.05.016.7838"},["b","8"],"And the lord commended the unjust steward, because he had done wisely: for the children of this world are in their generation wiser than the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"children"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"light"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.9","order":"03.05.016.7839"},["b","9"],"And I say unto you, Make to yourselves friends of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"mammon"],"of unrighteousness; that, when ye fail, they may receive you into everlasting habitations."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.10","order":"03.05.016.7840"},["b","10"],"He that is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"faithful"],"in that which is least is faithful also in much: and he that is unjust in the least is unjust also in much."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.11","order":"03.05.016.7841"},["b","11"],"If therefore ye have not been faithful in the unrighteous mammon, who will commit to your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"trust"],"the true",["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"riches"],"?"]],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.12","order":"03.05.016.7842"},["b","12"],"And if ye have not been faithful in that which is another man’s, who shall give you that which is your own?"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.13","order":"03.05.016.7843"},["b","13"],"¶No servant can serve two",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"masters"],": for either he will hate the one, and love the other; or else he will hold to the one, and despise the other. Ye cannot serve God and mammon."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.14","order":"03.05.016.7844"},["b","14"],"And the Pharisees also, who were",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"covetous"],", heard all these things: and they derided him."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15","order":"03.05.016.7845"},["b","15"],"And he said unto them, Ye are they which",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"justify"],"yourselves before men; but God",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"knoweth"],"your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"hearts"],": for that which is highly esteemed among",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_15d"},"men"],"is",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_15e"},"abomination"],"in the sight of God."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.16","order":"03.05.016.7846"},["b","16"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"The"],"law and the prophets",["i","were"],"until John: since that time the kingdom of God is preached, and every man presseth into it."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.17","order":"03.05.016.7847"},["b","17"],"And it is easier for heaven and earth to pass, than one tittle of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"law"],"to fail."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.18","order":"03.05.016.7848"},["b","18"],"Whosoever",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"putteth"],"away his wife, and marrieth another, committeth adultery: and whosoever marrieth her that is put away from",["i","her"],"husband committeth adultery."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.19","order":"03.05.016.7849"},["b","19"],"¶There was a certain rich man, which was clothed in purple and fine linen, and fared sumptuously every day:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.20","order":"03.05.016.7850"},["b","20"],"And there was a certain",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"beggar"],"named Lazarus, which was laid at his gate, full of sores,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.21","order":"03.05.016.7851"},["b","21"],"And desiring to be fed with the crumbs which fell from the rich man’s table: moreover the dogs came and licked his sores."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.22","order":"03.05.016.7852"},["b","22"],"And it came to pass, that the beggar died, and was carried by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"angels"],"into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"Abraham’s bosom"],": the rich man also died, and was buried;"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.23","order":"03.05.016.7853"},["b","23"],"And in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"hell"],"he lift up his eyes, being in torments, and seeth Abraham afar off, and Lazarus in his bosom."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.24","order":"03.05.016.7854"},["b","24"],"And he cried and said, Father Abraham, have mercy on me, and send Lazarus, that he may dip the tip of his finger in water, and cool my tongue; for I am tormented in this flame."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.25","order":"03.05.016.7855"},["b","25"],"But Abraham said, Son, remember that thou in thy lifetime",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"receivedst"],"thy good things, and likewise Lazarus evil things: but now he is comforted, and thou art tormented."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.26","order":"03.05.016.7856"},["b","26"],"And beside all this, between us and you there is a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"gulf"],"fixed: so that they which would pass from hence to you cannot; neither can they pass to us, that",["i","would come"],"from thence."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.27","order":"03.05.016.7857"},["b","27"],"Then he said, I pray thee therefore, father, that thou wouldest send him to my father’s house:"],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.28","order":"03.05.016.7858"},["b","28"],"For I have five brethren; that he may testify unto them, lest they also come into this place of torment."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.29","order":"03.05.016.7859"},["b","29"],"Abraham saith unto him, They have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"Moses"],"and the prophets; let them hear them."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.30","order":"03.05.016.7860"},["b","30"],"And he said, Nay, father Abraham: but if one went unto them from the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"dead"],", they will repent."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.31","order":"03.05.016.7861"},["b","31"],"And he said unto him, If they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"hear"],"not Moses and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"prophets"],", neither will they be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"persuaded"],", though one rose from the dead."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.1a","order":"03.05.016.7862"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/waste"},"TG Waste"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.2a","order":"03.05.016.7864"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.2b","order":"03.05.016.7866"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stewardship"},"TG Stewardship"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.8a","order":"03.05.016.7868"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/children-of-light"},"TG Children of Light"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.8b","order":"03.05.016.7870"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.9a","order":"03.05.016.7872"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.22"},"D&C 82:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.10a","order":"03.05.016.7874"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/25.21"},"Matt. 25:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/51.19"},"D&C 51:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.44,53"},"132:44, 53"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.11a","order":"03.05.016.7876"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/trustworthiness"},"TG Trustworthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.11b","order":"03.05.016.7878"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.13a","order":"03.05.016.7880"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.39.38-39"},"Alma 5:39 (38–39)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.14a","order":"03.05.016.7882"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/11.24.20,24"},"Alma 11:24 (20, 24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15a","order":"03.05.016.7884"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/10.29"},"Luke 10:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15b","order":"03.05.016.7886"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-intelligence-of"},"TG God, Intelligence of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-omniscience-of"},"God, Omniscience of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15c","order":"03.05.016.7888"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/21.2"},"Prov. 21:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"15d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15d","order":"03.05.016.7890"},["b","15d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.28.28-30"},"2 Ne. 9:28 (28–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.15e","order":"03.05.016.7892"},["b","15e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-natural-not-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, Natural, Not Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.16a","order":"03.05.016.7894"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-luke/16.16-23"},["span.small","JST"],"Luke 16:16–23 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.17a","order":"03.05.016.7896"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/law-of-moses"},"TG Law of Moses"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.18a","order":"03.05.016.7898"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"TG Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.20a","order":"03.05.016.7900"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/poor"},"TG Poor"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.22a","order":"03.05.016.7902"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.22b","order":"03.05.016.7904"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.11.11-21"},"Alma 40:11 (11–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.23a","order":"03.05.016.7906"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-in-prison"},"Spirits in Prison"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.25a","order":"03.05.016.7908"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.24"},"Luke 6:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.26a","order":"03.05.016.7910"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.28.28-30"},"1 Ne. 15:28 (28–30)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/separation"},"TG Separation"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.29a","order":"03.05.016.7912"},["b","29a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-value-of"},"TG Scriptures, Value of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.30a","order":"03.05.016.7914"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/32.18.17-18"},"Alma 32:18 (17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.12.12,18"},"Ether 12:12 (12, 18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.7.5-10"},"D&C 5:7 (5–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.31a","order":"03.05.016.7916"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-study-of"},"TG Scriptures, Study of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.31b","order":"03.05.016.7918"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/33.11.10-14"},"2 Ne. 33:11 (10–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/13.26.24-30"},"Hel. 13:26 (24–30)"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/16.31c","order":"03.05.016.7920"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.8.7-10"},"D&C 5:8 (7–10)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.71"},"133:71"],"."]]}
